Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Bosnia and the Dayton Agreement
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yktfk
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 24 Nov 1995
A possible end to the conflict in Bosnia, the role of the US in the peace treaty, and why the city of Dayton became the venue for the signing in November 1995.